column1: Weighted magnetic resonance image size (256, 256, 1) in T2, revealing the head of a man of 37 years old, with coronal section n°10 initiated from the back of the skull. The image reveals the presence of the white matter of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 862.2070 mm³, the cortex of left cerebral hemisphere of volume 2340.0879 mm³, the white matter of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 704.0039 mm³, the cortex of right cerebral hemisphere of volume 2115.9668 mm³ and the right cerebellar cortex of volume 188.5254 mm³.
